<manpage>
    <volume> 常用数据结构 </volume>
    <class>AStringBuf</class>
    <function> AStringBuf_&lt;length &gt; </function>

    <description>
        <para> 构造一个AStringBuf对象，并指定字符串字符数。</para>
    </description>

    <syntax_nopara>
        <apiname>AStringBuf_&lt;length &gt;</apiname>
    </syntax_nopara>   
    
    <remarks>
       <para>length长度中不包含'\0'字符。</para>
   </remarks>
<example>
<pre>
AStringBuf_&lt;20&gt; asbuf;    
ASSERT(asbuf.GetCapacity() == 20);
ASSERT(asbuf.GetLength() == 0);
ASSERT(asbuf.GetAvailableSpace() == 20);
</pre>
</example>   

